706
00:40:25,605 --> 00:40:27,147
- Pumunta sa kanya!
- Mabilis!

707
00:40:27,148 --> 00:40:28,441
<i>[Pagpapalakpak ng Seksyon E]</i>

708
00:40:32,362 --> 00:40:35,115
Kita mo? Nakikialam. Isang punto.

709
00:40:37,200 --> 00:40:38,118
magaling naman ako diba?

710
00:40:38,119 --> 00:40:40,286
Kung hindi ako nakikialam, hindi nila gagawin
magkaroon ng isa pang shot.

711
00:40:42,122 --> 00:40:43,623
aprubahan mo?

712
00:40:53,800 --> 00:40:54,800
Aries!

713
00:40:55,260 --> 00:40:57,344
Ano na ngayon?
Nagkaayos lang kami ni Ella.

714
00:40:57,345 --> 00:40:58,512
Kaya mo ba akong iwan mag-isa?

715
00:40:58,513 --> 00:40:59,681
Tingnan mo na lang ito.

716
00:41:00,306 --> 00:41:02,350
Alam mo, sa tingin ko ay hindi.

717
00:41:02,809 --> 00:41:03,977
Malamang si Ella yun.

718
00:41:04,352 --> 00:41:06,396
- Tandaan ang pangyayari?
- Oo!

719
00:41:07,772 --> 00:41:09,607
Sa tingin ko siya talaga.

720
00:41:09,774 --> 00:41:12,819
Siya lang ang meron ka
tumatawag ng kalapating mababa ang lipad.

721
00:41:13,987 --> 00:41:17,949
Alam mo. Matapang lang ang nararamdaman niya
dahil may Aries siya.

722
00:41:18,658 --> 00:41:19,700
<i>[Sumisigaw si Freya]</i>

723
00:41:19,701 --> 00:41:21,286
Nakakairita!

724
00:41:21,786 --> 00:41:24,454
Ikaw ang kalapating mababa ang lipad!
Si Ella ang kalapating mababa ang lipad!

725
00:41:24,622 --> 00:41:25,789
- Kita mo?
- Siya ay isang patutot!

726
00:41:25,790 --> 00:41:27,876
Tumigil ka, tumigil ka! Shh!

727
00:41:28,168 --> 00:41:31,421
Maaaring may isang tao
marinig ka ulit. Itigil mo na.

728
00:41:34,883 --> 00:41:37,051
Ano ang layunin niyan?
Bakit kailangan mong ipakita sa akin iyon?

729
00:41:37,052 --> 00:41:38,094
Patunay!

730
00:41:38,344 --> 00:41:40,554
Kahit kailan ay hindi tinawag ni Mica na patutot si Ella.

731
00:41:40,555 --> 00:41:42,974
At para idagdag pa.
Muli niyang sinabi.

732
00:41:43,850 --> 00:41:44,893
Anong gusto mong gawin ko?

733
00:41:46,227 --> 00:41:47,312
Hayaan mo na si Mica.

734
00:41:47,645 --> 00:41:48,645
Tapos na.

735
00:41:49,397 --> 00:41:50,647
Hoy, maghintay ka!

736
00:41:50,648 --> 00:41:51,857
Ano ang gusto mo ngayon?

737
00:41:51,858 --> 00:41:54,401
Hindi mo ba gagawin
parusahan si Freya dahil dito?

738
00:41:54,402 --> 00:41:56,154
Kailangan siyang turuan ng leksyon.

739
00:41:56,446 --> 00:41:57,446
yun lang.

740
00:41:57,906 --> 00:41:59,866
Gusto mo lang
balikan mo si Freya. tama?

741
00:42:00,492 --> 00:42:01,492
ha?

742
00:42:01,951 --> 00:42:02,619
Pero...

743
00:42:02,620 --> 00:42:05,622
Sinusubukan mo akong gamitin
para sa paghihiganti mo kay Freya.

744
00:42:06,623 --> 00:42:10,001
Gusto mo magalit ako kay Freya eh
bakit mo ako pinanood ng video. Tama?

745
00:42:10,376 --> 00:42:11,419
Hindi totoo yan!

746
00:42:13,963 --> 00:42:17,008
Dahil kung yan ang gusto mo,
tapos hindi ko paparusahan si Freya.

747
00:42:17,300 --> 00:42:20,804
At huwag na... kailanman subukan
gamitin mo ulit ako. Okay?

748
00:42:40,448 --> 00:42:43,201
<i>Kung sina Calix at Mica
nakuha ang kanilang pangalawang pagkakataon...</i>

749
00:42:43,785 --> 00:42:47,747
<i>posible ba para sa akin at kay Aries
para maayos din ang relasyon natin?</i>

750
00:42:51,918 --> 00:42:53,461
Hey. Miss.

751
00:43:03,847 --> 00:43:04,931
may kailangan ka ba?

752
00:43:05,390 --> 00:43:07,224
Umm... oo.

753
00:43:07,225 --> 00:43:08,642
Naliligaw talaga ako.

754
00:43:08,643 --> 00:43:11,563
Alam mo kung nasaan ang Eastwood Street?

755
00:43:12,272 --> 00:43:13,480
Ahhh...

756
00:43:13,481 --> 00:43:15,316
Ito ay maaaring ilagay sa akin sa isang atsara.

757
00:43:15,859 --> 00:43:16,901
Ehem...

758
00:43:18,903 --> 00:43:20,155
Diretso ka.

759
00:43:20,864 --> 00:43:22,115
Pagkatapos ay lumiko ka sa kanan.

760
00:43:22,782 --> 00:43:27,745
Tapos ikot-ikot ka, tapos
pagkatapos ng tatlong kanto, nakita mo ang bantay.

761
00:43:27,954 --> 00:43:30,248
Tapos tatanungin mo yung guard, "Guard, where's..."

762
00:43:30,707 --> 00:43:31,666
Ano ang..?

763
00:43:31,666 --> 00:43:32,625
Eastwood Street.

764
00:43:32,626 --> 00:43:34,878
"Guard, nasaan ang Eastwood Street?"

765
00:43:35,170 --> 00:43:35,712
Uh-huh.

766
00:43:35,713 --> 00:43:37,088
Pagkatapos ay malalaman mo ang sagot.

767
00:43:41,676 --> 00:43:42,676
Okay.

768
00:43:44,429 --> 00:43:45,305
Teka...

769
00:43:45,306 --> 00:43:46,598
Nakalimutan kong itanong ang pangalan mo.

770
00:43:48,349 --> 00:43:50,059
Ako si Jasper Jean...

771
00:44:08,912 --> 00:44:10,038
Sinong kausap mo?

772
00:44:10,580 --> 00:44:12,415
hindi ko alam. Tanong niya lang
para sa mga direksyon.

773
00:44:12,749 --> 00:44:13,917
Mayroon ka bang hanky?

774
00:44:14,083 --> 00:44:15,167
Hindi, bakit?

775
00:44:15,168 --> 00:44:18,129
Dumudugo yata ang ilong ko.
Nagsalita siya sa isang American accent.

776
00:44:19,964 --> 00:44:20,798
Bumaba ka na!

777
00:44:20,798 --> 00:44:21,549
Huh, bakit?

778
00:44:21,550 --> 00:44:22,634
Bumaba ka na lang!

779
00:44:25,512 --> 00:44:26,888
Hoy! Hoy, teka!

780
00:44:27,931 --> 00:44:30,934
Oh, ganyan ang gusto mong maglaro.
Sumakay ka sa bisikleta, sasakay ako nito!

781
00:44:31,100 --> 00:44:32,310
Sir, tara na.

782
00:44:32,727 --> 00:44:33,727
Sundan mo siya.

783
00:44:36,522 --> 00:44:37,774
Ito ay masaya.

784
00:44:48,576 --> 00:44:49,619
At pababa.

785
00:44:50,620 --> 00:44:51,620
Hoy, Yuri!

786
00:44:52,705 --> 00:44:54,581
Binalikan mo na ako.
Huwag itulak ang iyong suwerte.

787
00:44:54,582 --> 00:44:56,742
Ito ay hindi sapat.
Ilabas natin ito sa kabila!

788
00:44:56,834 --> 00:44:57,918
Mahal kita, David ko.

789
00:44:57,919 --> 00:44:59,587
- Mahal din kita. paalam.
- Napakagulo.

790
00:45:00,713 --> 00:45:01,589
Oh?

791
00:45:01,714 --> 00:45:02,799
may girlfriend ka na?

792
00:45:03,883 --> 00:45:04,883
tama yan.

793
00:45:05,510 --> 00:45:07,887
So Casanova ka rin ha?

794
00:45:08,179 --> 00:45:10,180
Teka, pare. Kailangan kong umihi.
Sandali lang.

795
00:45:10,181 --> 00:45:11,181
Oo naman.

796
00:45:11,641 --> 00:45:12,849
Okay lang bang hindi mag-inat?

797
00:45:12,850 --> 00:45:14,811
- Oo.
- Ang sakit na ng katawan ko.

798
00:45:17,939 --> 00:45:18,939
Keif.

799
00:45:22,986 --> 00:45:24,362
Parang nakita ko si Percy.

800
00:45:24,946 --> 00:45:27,115
Hayaan mo siyang magpahinga nang mapayapa, Yuri.

801
00:45:27,740 --> 00:45:30,159
Guys! Nandito na si Miss Asunta!

802
00:45:30,368 --> 00:45:32,411
- Magandang umaga, ginang.
- Magandang umaga!

803
00:45:32,412 --> 00:45:36,291
Section E, ano na?
Nag-stretch na ba kayo?

804
00:45:36,666 --> 00:45:38,000
Oo, Ma'am.

805
00:45:38,001 --> 00:45:39,001
buti naman.

806
00:45:39,043 --> 00:45:41,753
Magsasagawa kami ng 500-meter run ngayon.

807
00:45:41,754 --> 00:45:42,754
Ito ang iyong warm-up.

808
00:45:43,131 --> 00:45:47,718
Pagbalik ko, siguraduhin mo
nakakondisyon na ang mga katawan para tumakbo.

809
00:45:47,719 --> 00:45:49,554
- Ayos ba tayo niyan?
- Oo!

810
00:45:49,762 --> 00:45:51,764
Mabuti. See you later.

811
00:45:52,932 --> 00:45:53,933
Sir John!

812
00:45:54,434 --> 00:45:55,434
Oo?

813
00:45:55,643 --> 00:45:57,520
Pinapatawag kami sa Principal's Office.

814
00:45:57,687 --> 00:46:00,648
Sige, darating.
Freya, manguna ka.

815
00:46:03,026 --> 00:46:05,068
Isa, dalawa, tatlo, apat,

816
00:46:05,069 --> 00:46:06,611
lima, anim, pito, walo.

817
00:46:06,612 --> 00:46:07,905
Tatakbo tayo, pare.

818
00:46:08,114 --> 00:46:09,656
Tatlo, apat, lima

819
00:46:09,657 --> 00:46:12,118
- Hulihin mo ako!
- Hoy, bata! Ibalik mo yan!

820
00:46:14,203 --> 00:46:16,080
Damn it, ibigay mo dito!

821
00:46:16,497 --> 00:46:18,958
Hoy! Lumipat,
wala sa daan!

822
00:46:19,500 --> 00:46:21,140
Tingnan natin kung ikaw
mabilis lang, Jay-jay!

823
00:46:21,169 --> 00:46:22,295
Hi, Jay!

824
00:46:24,130 --> 00:46:25,631
Kiko, pakiusap.

825
00:46:26,591 --> 00:46:28,301
Guys, focus ako.

826
00:46:28,968 --> 00:46:29,968
Ah!

827
00:46:30,762 --> 00:46:33,014
<i>[Seksyon E tumatawa]</i>

828
00:46:38,311 --> 00:46:39,645
Ooh!

829
00:46:39,646 --> 00:46:41,647
- Siya ay tapos na para sa.
- Damn, pare.

830
00:46:42,398 --> 00:46:43,649
Nagkamali ka.

831
00:46:43,733 --> 00:46:45,026
Darating ang away ng magkasintahan!

832
00:46:45,401 --> 00:46:47,195
- Anong nangyari?
- Anong meron sa kanya?

833
00:46:47,904 --> 00:46:50,197
- Yuri, pakalmahin mo siya.
- Magagalit na naman siya.

834
00:46:50,198 --> 00:46:52,074
- Magkano ang gusto mong taya?
- Limang libo.

835
00:46:52,075 --> 00:46:53,075
ikaw naman?

836
00:46:53,326 --> 00:46:54,619
Ipinupusta ko ang pera ko kay Jay-jay.

837
00:47:02,710 --> 00:47:04,420
Ano bang nangyayari sayo?!

838
00:47:05,755 --> 00:47:06,964
Ikaw ang may kasalanan!

839
00:47:08,466 --> 00:47:12,053
Baliw kang babae ka!

840
00:47:12,220 --> 00:47:13,054
Jay, tumakbo ka!

841
00:47:13,055 --> 00:47:14,180
Tumakbo para sa iyong buhay!

842
00:47:15,056 --> 00:47:15,973
Kunin mo siya!

843
00:47:15,974 --> 00:47:17,516
<i>[Section E cheering for Jay-jay]</i>

844
00:47:17,517 --> 00:47:18,517
Kunin mo siya!

845
00:47:28,027 --> 00:47:29,444
Paikutin siya hanggang sa maging violet siya!

846
00:47:29,445 --> 00:47:30,821
Ibaba mo ako!

847
00:47:30,822 --> 00:47:31,822
Go!

848
00:47:32,782 --> 00:47:34,367
anong ginagawa mo
Ibaba mo ako!

849
00:47:43,209 --> 00:47:44,335
Ano ba naman!

850
00:47:48,047 --> 00:47:49,548
Naghalikan sila!

851
00:47:49,549 --> 00:47:51,592
<i>[Pagpapalakpak ng Seksyon E]</i>

852
00:47:53,719 --> 00:47:56,222
Nag-aklas na naman ang mag-asawa!

853
00:47:56,556 --> 00:47:57,807
Sinadya mo yun.

854
00:47:58,433 --> 00:47:59,559
Hindi, hindi ko ginawa!

855
00:48:00,476 --> 00:48:02,228
Jay-jay! may problema ba

856
00:48:02,603 --> 00:48:03,771
Bumalik ka na sa section mo.

857
00:48:06,399 --> 00:48:07,399
Tara na.

858
00:48:08,860 --> 00:48:09,527
Ah— Aray...

859
00:48:09,528 --> 00:48:10,944
- Alisin mo ang iyong mga kamay sa akin!
- Hayaan mo.

860
00:48:10,945 --> 00:48:11,945
Gawin mo ako.

861
00:48:12,488 --> 00:48:13,948
Ah! Bitawan mo ako!

862
00:48:14,240 --> 00:48:14,782
Hindi!

863
00:48:15,074 --> 00:48:16,241
Aray! Nasasaktan ako!

864
00:48:16,242 --> 00:48:17,951
Pakakawalan ba kayong dalawa!
Nasasaktan ako dito!

865
00:48:17,952 --> 00:48:19,094
Bakit ang iyong pag-aalala?

866
00:48:19,203 --> 00:48:20,328
Pinsan ko siya!

867
00:48:20,329 --> 00:48:21,329
nag-aalala ako!

868
00:48:21,330 --> 00:48:22,456
What the hell?

869
00:48:22,457 --> 00:48:24,040
Ano bang problema mo!

870
00:48:24,041 --> 00:48:26,042
Ito ay wala sa iyong negosyo!
Siya ay kabilang sa Section E!

871
00:48:26,043 --> 00:48:27,211
- Hindi!
- Aray!

872
00:48:30,923 --> 00:48:33,092
<i>Maglagay ng tang sa baso!</i>

873
00:49:42,161 --> 00:49:42,787
Okay ka lang ba, Jay?

874
00:49:42,788 --> 00:49:44,308
Walang ibig sabihin sa akin ang halik na iyon.

875
00:49:44,413 --> 00:49:45,998
Baka kailangan mo ng Kisspirin.

876
00:49:46,457 --> 00:49:47,541
O isang Yakapsul.

877
00:49:47,542 --> 00:49:49,460
Basahin nang mabuti ang mga tagubilin.

878
00:49:50,127 --> 00:49:52,045
Maraming tao ang nagkakamali kahit na
kapag tama ang sagot nila,

879
00:49:52,046 --> 00:49:53,965
dahil hindi nila sinunod ang mga direksyon.

880
00:49:54,590 --> 00:49:55,591
<i>[Umuungol si Jay-jay]</i>

881
00:49:59,679 --> 00:50:00,929
Nag-alok ka ng pagkain pero hindi luto.

882
00:50:00,930 --> 00:50:02,181
Pagkatapos ay i-bake ito.

883
00:50:03,516 --> 00:50:04,916
- Siya ba ang isa?
- Oo, siya iyon!

884
00:50:05,518 --> 00:50:06,768
Ninakaw niya.

885
00:50:06,769 --> 00:50:07,395
Bata...

886
00:50:07,396 --> 00:50:08,813
nasaan ang pera ng girlfriend ko?

887
00:50:09,021 --> 00:50:10,438
- Hindi mo alam?!
- Hoy! Hoy!

888
00:50:10,439 --> 00:50:11,481
Alisin mo ang kamay mo kay Ci-N!

889
00:50:11,482 --> 00:50:12,650
Isipin ang iyong sariling negosyo!

890
00:50:12,942 --> 00:50:14,818
Ninakaw ng lalaking iyon ang pera ko!

891
00:50:14,819 --> 00:50:16,279
Ay naku...

892
00:50:16,404 --> 00:50:18,697
Ci-N. Ginawa mo ulit?

893
00:50:18,698 --> 00:50:21,575
Parang napatunayan mo na
totoo ang sinasabi nila!

894
00:50:21,576 --> 00:50:22,702
Jay-jay!

895
00:50:22,994 --> 00:50:23,494
Shit!

896
00:50:23,495 --> 00:50:24,537
Huminahon ka!

897
00:50:24,912 --> 00:50:25,955
Shh!

898
00:50:26,372 --> 00:50:27,665
Titigil ka ba sa pagtawa?

899
00:50:27,999 --> 00:50:30,459
Ang paghingi ng tawad ay hindi ko bagay.
Ganun din ang pagpapaliwanag.

900
00:50:30,793 --> 00:50:33,336
Babayaran ko ang kabuuan ng cafe
kita para sa araw.

901
00:50:33,337 --> 00:50:34,897
Paalisin mo na lang lahat ng customer dito.

902
00:50:35,047 --> 00:50:36,757
Lalo na yung mga mapanghusga.

